ResourceHeader.ResourceName: MAVEN SEP Calibrated Ion and Electron Spectra Data Collection (Sensor 1)

RevisionEvent.Note: Draft metadata created by LFB (ADAPT code), final editing by AK

ResourceHeader.Description: Calibrated MAVEN Solar Energetic Particle (SEP) Instrument Sensor 1 ion and electron spectra. The data include total (integrated) and differential (as a function of 28 energy windows) ion and electron number fluxes in forward and reverse look directions. Description of the SEP instrument can be found on the SEP home page https://lasp.colorado.edu/maven/science/instrument-package/sep/ and in the SEP instrument publication https://doi.org/10.1007/s11214-015-0218-z.
ResourceHeader.Acknowledgement: Please acknowledge the Principal Investigator D. Larson for use of these data.
